'''Makka''' nɣ '''Mkka''' (s [[Tutlayt Taɛrabt|taɛrabt]]: مكة) tga yat tamdint illan ɣ utaram n tmazirt n Ssaɛudiyya, taggug f [[Almadina Almunawwara|Tamdint Ifawn]] s kran 4000 kilumitr ɣ umnid n iffus ataram, d f tɣrmt [[Ṭṭayf]] s kran n 1200 kilumiṭr ɣ amnid acrqi, d f 72 kilumitr zɣ tiɣrmt n [[Jadda]] d aftas n y[[Ill Azggaɣ|ill azggaɣ]]. 

Tga Makka Lmukarrama yat tmdint tasgdant bahra ilan atig dar [[Lislam|imuslmn]]. Tlla gis [[Timzgida n lḥaram|timzgida n Lḥaram]], d [[Lkɛba|Lkaɛba]] nna ygan lqblt n imuslmn ɣ [[Taẓallit|tẓallit]] nnsn.

